    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <pb xml:id="leaf001r" facs="loc.03632.001_large.jpg" type="recto"/>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place">Simpson, Spence &amp; Young</name>
                    <name type="place">88 Monte Rosa</name>
                    <name type="place">Arrow line wharf</name>
                    <name type="place">23rd Street</name>
                    <name type="place">New York—</name>
                    <name type="place">N.R—</name>
                </dateline>
                <salute>Dear Sir,</salute>
            </opener>
            <p>My brother Ernest Rhys<ptr target="n4152"/> has given me a letter of 
                introduction to you.<ptr target="n5002d"/> Our visit 
                to America is a very short one. We leave early tomorrow for a little 
                tour including Niagara &amp; will not be home to our steamer till 
                Saturday night.</p>
            <p>The Captain says we may have to leave on Tuesday or Wednesday. So we 
                have only Monday on which we can <unclear reason="damage" cert="high" resp="#me">avail</unclear> 
                ourselves of the privilege of seeing you—if 
                <pb xml:id="leaf001v" facs="loc.03632.002_large.jpg" type="verso"/>
                therefore you can be troubled with a visit from two girls who would 
                dearly like to see you, we will come on that day—Ernest said 
                M<hi rend="underline">r</hi> Gilchrist<ptr target="n0262"/> would be 
                at Camden, but he gave us no address.</p>
            <p>Hoping <unclear reason="damage" cert="medium" resp="#me">we</unclear> shall 
                <unclear reason="damage" cert="medium" resp="#me">not</unclear> return to 
                England disappointed at not seeing you</p>
            <closer>
                <salute>Believe me</salute>
                <salute>Sincerely yours</salute>
                <signed>Edith R<unclear reason="illegible" resp="#smb" cert="low">hys</unclear>—</signed>
            </closer>
        </body>
    </text>
